|date=2015-03-16|last=Bibel|first=Sara|publisher=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|accessdate=2015-03-16|archive-date=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319214810/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/03/16/scripted-drama-unreal-to-premiere-monday-june-1-on-lifetime/375463/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2015年7月6日，Lifetime宣布續訂本劇第2季10集，並於2016年夏季回歸。<ref name="Season 2 renew">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/lifetime-renews-unreal-second-season-806927 |title=Lifetime Renews ''Unreal'' for Second Season |work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]] |first=Michael |last=O'Connell |date=2015-07-06 |accessdate=2015-07-06 |archive-date=2019-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007235813/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/lifetime-renews-unreal-second-season-806927 |dead-url=no }}</ref>9月4日，宣布《{{le|女法官艾米|Judging Amy}}》{{link-en|卡蘿·芭比|Carol Barbee}}將於第2季加入製作陣容，為她和瑪蒂·納克森繼《{{le|閨蜜離婚指南|Girlfriends' Guide to Divorce}}》後再度合作，而主編劇史黛西·魯凱澤（{{lang|en|Stacy Rukeyser}}）亦被提升為執行製作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/lifetimes-unreal-bolsters-creative-team-811279|title=Lifetime's 'UnREAL' Bolsters Creative Team|date=2015-09-04|author=Lesley Goldberg|publisher=好萊塢報導|accessdate=2017-03-09|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211210912/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/lifetimes-unreal-bolsters-creative-team-811279|dead-url=no}}</ref>

