rs-female-suitor-lifetime/|title=''UnREAL'' Season 3 Scoop: ''Everlasting'' Is Getting Its First Female Suitor|author=Dave Nemetz|publisher=TVLine|date=2016-11-01|accessdate=2017-03-09|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221024143/https://tvline.com/2016/11/01/unreal-season-3-spoilers-female-suitor-lifetime/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年4月7日，季默在個人[[Twitter|Twitter]]上透露第3季將延後至2018年初播出。<ref name="Season 3 Delay">{{Cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2017/06/04/unreal-season-3-delayed-premiering-2018-lifetime/|title=''UnREAL'' Season 3 Delayed Until 2018|author=Dave Nemetz|publisher=TVLine|date=2017-06-04|accessdate=2017-06-04|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128050502/https://tvline.com/2017/06/04/unreal-season-3-delayed-premiering-2018-lifetime/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月28日，Lifetime在[[電視評論家協會|電視評論家協會]]上提前宣布續訂第4季。<ref name="Season 4">{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/07/unreal-renewed-season-4-lifetime-mary-kills-season-2-people-tca-1202137915/|title=‘UnReal’ Renewed For Season 4 On Lifetime; Rookie ‘Mary Kills People’ Also Picked Up – TCA|author=Erik Pedersen|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2017-07-28|accessdate=2017-07-28|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212182903/https://deadline.com/2017/07/unreal-renewed-season-4-lifetime-mary-kills-season-2-people-tca-1202137915/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第3季導演陣容包括數名女性導演，艾波比與主創雪佩洛將再次執導演筒，季默則獻出導演處女作，其他亦有《[[嘻哈帝國|嘻哈世家]]》{{le|哈妮兒·考佩珀|Hanelle Culpepper|哈妮兒·M·考佩珀}}與《[[異世奇人|超時空奇俠]]》{{le|雪莉·佛克森|Sheree Folkson}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/10/unreal-season-3-premiere-date-caitlin-fitzgerald-shiri-appleby-constance-zimmer-1202190049/|title=‘UnReal’ Gets Season 3 Trailer & Premiere Date; Caitlin FitzGerald Cast As Suitress|author=Erik Pedersen|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2017-10-17|accessdate=2017-10-17|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211204339/https://deadline.com/2017/10/unreal-season-3-premiere-date-caitlin-fitzgerald-shiri-appleby-constance-zimmer-1202190049/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第3季於2017年5月製作完成，第4季則從2017年10月拍攝至2018年1月。<ref name="Hulu"/>

