《虛幻》獲得了廣泛的好評。<ref name=Yahoo-PaleyLive-UnREAL-2015>{{cite news|last1=[[Paley_Center_for_Media|Paley Center for Media]]|title=PaleyLive: An Evening with the Cast & Creators of UnREAL|url=https://screen.yahoo.com/popular/paleylive-evening-cast-creators-unreal-160000845.html|accessdate=2015-08-01|work=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]|date=2015-07-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019104937/https://screen.yahoo.com/popular/paleylive-evening-cast-creators-unreal-160000845.html|archivedate=2015-10-19}}</ref>[[福布斯|福布斯]]的美蘿·巴爾（{{lang|en|Merrill Barr}}）稱本劇「是夏天最佳的新節目，因為它將瘋狂的一面呈現在銀幕上」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/merrillbarr/2015/05/25/unreal-tv-series/ |title=''UnREAL'' Review: The Drama Lifetime Was Born To Make Arrives In Insane Glory |first=Merrill |last=Barr |work=[[福布斯|福布斯]] |date=2015-05-25 |accessdate=2015-06-10 |archive-date=2019-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021161257/https://www.forbes.com/sites/merrillbarr/2015/05/25/unreal-tv-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>娛樂周刊的戴琳·羅芬史汀（{{lang|en|Dalene Rovenstine}}）寫道「如果你喜歡《[[鑽石求千金|鑽石求千金]]》，你就會愛上《虛幻》」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/recap/unreal-series-premiere |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610170144/http://www.ew.com/recap/unreal-series-premiere |title=Lifetime's scripted drama about a reality dating show goes deliciously dark |first=Dalene |last=Rovenstine |work=娛樂周刊 |date=2015-06-01 |accessdate=2015-06-10 |archivedate=2015-06-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]的強·卡萊梅尼卡（{{lang|en|Jon Caramanica}}）寫到本劇帶出了「尖酸刻薄又無情傷感」及「非常符合卻有時很可悲的了解到女人何苦為難女人的道理」。<ref name="NYT Caramanica">{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/01/arts/television/lifetimes-unreal-traces-the-cracks-in-reality-tvs-fourth-wall.html? |title=Lifetime’s ''UnREAL'' Traces the Cracks in Reality TV’s Fourth Wall |first=Jon |last=Caramanica |work=紐約時報 |date=2015-05-31 |accessdate=2015-06-10 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925045106/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/01/arts/television/lifetimes-unreal-traces-the-cracks-in-reality-tvs-fourth-wall.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年12月，娛樂周刊的傑夫·詹森（{{lang|en|Jeff Jensen}}）將本劇名列於「2015年10大最佳新節目」榜單中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/gallery/best-new-shows-2015-jeff-jensen-picks/2406448_8-unreal-lifetime |title=The 10 Best New Shows of 2015: Jeff Jensen's Picks |work=娛樂周刊 |first=Jeff |last=Jensen |date=2015-12-09 |accessdate=2015-12-28 |archive-date=2017-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620034647/http://ew.com/gallery/best-new-shows-2015-jeff-jensen-picks/2406448_8-unreal-lifetime/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

